{"type":"message","id":"11f513e8","parentId":"54b3fb19","timestamp":"2026-03-17T11:05:00.997Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d Context Monitor] powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\miliger-context-manager\\scripts\\context-monitor.ps1\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 17th, 2026 — 19:05 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-17 11:05 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1773745500996}}
